Package io.jans.scim.service.antlr.scimFilter.antlr4

Interface ScimFilterListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FilterListener, ScimFilterBaseListener
    public interface ScimFilterListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by ScimFilterParser.
